<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">为扎实开展党纪学习教育，让全体党员受警醒、明底线、知敬畏，5月7日，学校组织党员干部赴江西省洪城监狱开展警示教育。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-08%2014%3A13%3A35111.jpg?Expires=2030508815&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=re1zJ30nf0azKM%2BlGKN3QxZ1ozs%3D" alt="" width="650" height="391" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">在讲解员的带领和解说下，大家依次参观工作区、监舍、活动区等场所，观看服刑人员接受改造图文展示及警示教育片，现场聆听服刑人员的现身说法。大家真实感受服刑人员痛彻心扉的深刻忏悔，深切体会到失去自由的痛苦和违法犯罪的沉重代价，接受了最直观、最深刻的廉洁警示教育，既涤荡了心灵，也净化了灵魂。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">大家纷纷表示，今后会时时以案为鉴、以人为镜，坚守底线、严守纪律，常思贪欲之害、常怀律己之心，积极投身党纪学习教育，认真学习《中国共产党纪律处分条例》，做到学纪、知纪、明纪、守纪，把遵规守纪刻印在心，并内化为言行准则，主动养成在监督和约束下学习、工作与生活的习惯。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">今后，我校将持续推进党规党纪学习，引导党员干部坚决把思想和行动统一到党中央决策部署上来，切实把纪律处分条例学习好、贯彻好、执行好，积极发扬自我革命精神；坚决纠治形式主义、官僚主义，积极落实过紧日子的要求，强化纪律教育、廉洁教育、正反典型教育；推动党员干部树牢遵规守纪的思想自觉、行动自觉，以干部作风能力建设新成效，推动学校工作高质量发展。</span></p><p><br/></p>